have two terms,

00:03:47.125 --> 00:03:50.020
but it may have
many, many terms.

00:03:50.020 --> 00:03:53.109
With that said, this is
not the defining property.

00:03:53.109 --> 00:03:54.650
This is really the
defining property,

00:03:54.650 --> 00:03:57.940
whether your a
boson or a fermion.

