theory, just the bare basics.

00:07:34.135 --> 00:07:36.340
It's pretty straightforward.

00:07:36.340 --> 00:07:39.319
But it's a beautiful thing about
relativistic quantum mechanics,

00:07:39.319 --> 00:07:40.860
so I'm going to turn
this all around.

00:07:40.860 --> 00:07:42.430
So let's look at the history.

00:07:42.430 --> 00:07:44.760
The history of this was people
looked at atomic spectra

00:07:44.760 --> 00:07:46.165
